metadata.name: Mar Cravo
metadata.description:
Combining original photography and artificial intelligence, Mar Cravo presents a red carnation, an enduring emblem of the Carnation Revolution, rooted at the intersection of freedom, collaboration, and love, encapsulating the historical resilience of Lisbon and its surrounding waters. 

The work symbolizes the fusion of historical events and natural elements with the innovative realm of technology. This piece exists in the revolutionary domain of blockchain, uniting the past, present, and future in a unique digital manifesto. Expanding beyond our own reality and into a psychedelic natural world sheds restriction and embraces a divine moment of bliss.
